[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
Hoang's father fires rapidly at Kai. The kid starts to scream. I grab him and the unconcious woman to the next room, trying my best not to look behind.[p]
Kai can't die like this. Kai won't die like this. Stay focus, An. This is when a nurse has to do her job.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

