[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#Hoang
What...what happened? Why are you guys here? Is Dr Quang dead? Did i...did i kill him?[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#An
It's ok, Dr Quang is going to be fine. Baby, look at me. We can handle this.[p]
Dr Quang and i are going to get you out of here. Trust me. Cover your ears if those gun shots scare you, please.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

