#Kai
Awww, there were so many, so many other ways that i could have handled this.[p]
I could have made that useless mouth of yours not being able to utter a single word from the begining. But i won't. For the kid's sake.[p]
This visit to the human world and the whole doctor thing changed me more than i expected. So i'll just play with you until the police arrive. [p]
Consider this as a token of gratitude, my "love" for you[p]
[_tb_end_text]

