[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
Kai and Hoang disappear.[p]
I do all the things Kai said, explain everything with the police, ambulance and firefighters until midnight.[p]
There's no survivor found in the exploision. But the police found many weapons, heroine and a long list of criminal papers in the house.[p]
Mr. Phat and his cooperation are put into investigation. After finishing everything with the police, i return to the hospital to see Kai sleeping next to Hoang's bed.[p]
The TV is representing the news the news about the exploision.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

