Are they ok now?[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#Miss Kim
The operation was successful. Both of them were just too tired i guess.[p]
Dr. Quang told everyone everything. You two made the right choice getting the kid out of there. What an awful household.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_tyrano_code]
