[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#Miss Kim
You know, An. You have came a long way since your first day here. At first no one thought you will last through the Internship.[p]
Now here you are, gaining trust from the patients and colleagues. You also aren't stuck with the charity fund department anymore.[p]
He was right to put his trust in you.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#An
Aww, i love everyone at the charity department. And thank you miss Kim, i appreciate it.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

