I smile at the kind lady and gently stroke Kai's hair. I can't be where i am today without him putting trust in me.[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
But Kai...[p]
My heart suddenly feels so heavy[p]
...Just what happened with you tonight? Why were you...?[p]
[_tb_end_text]

